declare_type_abbrev("JUDG", [], ”(STAMP ¸ AUTH ¸ AUTH SET ¸ SENT) + (AUTH SET)®);
=TEX

A special authority called $â$ (bottom) may be used without signature, and is therefore untrustworthy.

